[[!tag Energy_Drink Review]]

Founded by Lance Collins, the founder of Nos, Fuze, premium water brand Core,
and BodyArmor, Ashoc is an energy drink that positions itself as a natural,
clean, zero-sugar alternative to high-sugar energy drinks. Previously it was
known as Adrenaline Shoc but that was eventually shortened to just Ashoc. I
found it because it's $1.25 at the Dollar Tree.

<figure>
[[!template id="hooya-img.tmpl" cid="bafkreiboudkjgze6jm42lem3qnsut5ylyj36lzou3y2cssyneip2jvxw3m" size=medium]]
